summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of West Andover Street from 22 "Avenue S.W. to 19" Avenue S.W. et al in the City of Seattle, by constructing watermains under Ordinance No. 25356, creating Local Improvement District No. 2411 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
